= Action name = PCK.AUTOMIC_CA_VERACODE.PUB.ACTION.GET_PRESCAN_RESULTS
= General description = This action fetches the results of the pre-scan.
= Failure Conditions = * If the user does not have access to the specified application id, sandboxid or build Id. * If no prescan has been performed on the specified application id yet. * If the user has specified a non-existing application id, sandboxid or build Id.
= Inputs = * Application ID : Provide ID of the prescanned application. E.g. 384912 * Build ID : Provide Build ID of the prescan. If empty system gets recent prescan results. Validations: Build ID can only be numeric. E.g. 1797857 * Sandbox ID : Enter the ID of the sandbox if you performed a sandbox scan. Validations: Sandbox ID can only be numeric. E.g. 481409
= Behavior = (none)
=Return Value= * UC4RB_VER_RESPONSE: prescanresults XML content.
= Outputs = * Return code is 0 in case of success. * Return code is non-zero in case of failure.
= Rollback = (none)
= Logging = AE logs will be displayed in the AE report.
= Example = * Application ID : 384912 * Build ID : 1797857 * Sandbox ID : 481409
